---
title: Chicken Breast & Creamy Oregano Sauce with Rosemary-Roasted Potatoes & Garlicky Veggies
description: It’s all about the sauce in this winning dinner – garlic and oregano combine in a creamy and delectable sauce that’s rich and
indulgent. Teamed with succulent chicken, rosemary potatoes and garlicky veggies, you just can’t go wrong.
